Introduction

Yoo Youngseo is a South Korean singer under PocketDol Studio. He is a member of the boy group BAE173 and the co-ed project group A-SIX.

On September 26, 2024, he was revealed as a contestant on JTBC's survival show PROJECT7, which started in October 2024. He was eliminated in the final after ranking 17th place.
